        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Dr Joshua/Jessie Waggoner: Tremere Curse and Cursed Item Officanado. They grew up Serious, with little time for magic or superstitions. Their family home was Old, with bad plumbing, that was all. And anyone who believed the twoddle about a Ghost haunting the place showed that they themselves weren't fit to be called Adults. They purused an academic career in the sciences. However, when the death of their parents called them Back to their family home, they had an experience that scared the skepticism right out of them. After that night, they believed, and realized that there was only one thing for it, they needed to learn more. They scoured the city for knowledge of spirits, and hauntings, which only made them believe that the house had not been Truly haunted after all, but rather that it had been Cursed. And that realization opened a Floodgate in their mind. They suddenly needed to know everything they could about such things. How they worked, how they could be destroyed, and How they came to be. In their search for knowledge, they contacted a Tremere, who realized that this person's growing knowledge of Curses was an asset just waiting to be put to good use, either for or against them. So they were brought into the clan, and now they use their garnered information for the benefit thereof. Their old house still stands, and another family has been having similar trouble as they did. They've also begun to have this odd and somewhat troubling desire that, in addition to learning about accursed items, they are beginning to Need to create one."
        ],
